{"metadata": {"description": "Get a head-start in trades training! This youth program is perfect for those looking to build their skills and experience in a specific trade while attending high school.", "robots": "index, follow", "og:site_name": "SkilledTradesBC", "og:type": "landing-page", "og:url": "https://skilledtradesbc.ca/youth-train-in-trades-program", "og:title": "Youth Train in Trades Program | SkilledTradesBC", "og:description": "Get a head-start in trades training! This youth program is perfect for those looking to build their skills and experience in a specific trade while attending high school.", "twitter:card": "summary_large_image", "twitter:description": "Get a head-start in trades training! This youth program is perfect for those looking to build their skills and experience in a specific trade while attending high school.", "twitter:site": "@SkilledTradesBC", "Generator": "Drupal 11 (https://www.drupal.org)", "MobileOptimized": "width", "HandheldFriendly": "true", "viewport": "width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0", "title": "Youth Train in Trades Program | SkilledTradesBC"}, "markdown": "Skip to main content\n\n###### Menu\n\n____ Show/hide collapsed content\n\nSkilledTradesBC and the BC Ministry of Education and Child Care (ECC) teamed up to offer funding for students to complete their technical training while still in high school. \n\nStudents can receive credits towards their high school diploma and at least one level of technical training by attending trades training classes at local high schools, post-secondary institutions, or SkilledTradesBC-certified training facilities. \n\n**Program Application Guide and Timelines**\n\n[Youth Train in Trades Guide - 2023](/media/1795/download)\n\nForms and Resources\n\n[Youth Train in Trades Registration Form](/media/1764/download)\n\n[Youth Technical Training Result Report](/media/1761/download)\n\n[Youth Train in Trades Aircraft Maintenance Technician Results Report](/media/1174/download)\n\nResources f